<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New Response on Support Ticket</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
    <p>You have received a new response on your support ticket:</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p><strong>Ticket Number:</strong> <%= ticketNumber %></p>
        <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= subject %></p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background-color: #e8f4f8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;">
        <p><strong>Support Response:</strong></p>
        <p><%= message %></p>
    </div>
    
    <p>You can reply to this ticket by logging into your account.</p>
    
    <p>Thank you,<br>Recyleto Support Team</p>
</body>
</html>